home.row1-1: 《技能大乱斗》是一款自动对战游戏，融合了《自走棋》、《原子战争》、《孽主》等游戏的乐趣，与《Ability Draft》的深度和多样性。请访问我们的 {link} 以了解更多信息。
home.row2-2: 混合匹配法术以打造酷炫组合
home.row2-3: 无需考虑经济因素 - 你的金币将每回合重置一次
home.row2-5: 游戏中有 150 种法术，每场游戏将随机禁用 50 种
home.row2-6: 游戏中的每个法术都有 20 个副本，所有玩家共享相同的法术池
home.row8-2: 购买重复法术以提高法术点数
home.row8-3: 3 点 = 标准级别法术（等同于 Dota 中的最大等级）
home.row8-4: 6 点 = 超级级别法术（可提供力量天赋、魔晶或物品）
home.row8-5: 9 点 = G 胖级别法术（有点狂）
home.row8-6: 英雄将尝试按照从左至右的顺序施放法术
home.row3-2: 游戏中提供了多种神可供挑选，每个神都有自己的独特技能和协同作用
home.row3-3: 打开神之宝箱以解锁新神，同时每个月还可通过战斗通行证进行解锁
home.row3-4: 神来源于多个 Valve 宇宙。谁会是下一个呢？
home.row4-2: 英雄身体将在游戏过程中周期性提供
home.row4-3: 身体将按照力量水平划分为多个层次（S、A、B、C、D）
home.row4-4: 花费 2 金币可重新选择身体
home.row4-5: 常规 Dota 饰品将免费纳入
home.row4-6: 英雄等级将与当前回合数相同
home.row5-2: 战斗通行证可提供免费奖励。购买战斗通行证以获得更多奖励！
home.row5-3: 每个赛季都会有新的战斗通行证，提供全新奖励，包括新的神、竞技场、终结技等等！
home.row5-4: 竞技场 - 更改战场外观
home.row5-5: 终结技 - 更改神向敌人投出的伤害投掷物
home.row5-6: 宝箱 - 打开宝箱可获得奖励，包括神的帽子
home.row6-2: 游戏开始时 +1 神之插槽
home.row6-4: 可获得每月轮换的 PLUS 专属神
home.row6-7: 1 额外翻倍奖励（每周冷却）
home.row7-3: 每个赛季都会有法术进行轮换
home.row7-4: 每次更新战斗通行证时都会添加新的神和饰品
home.row7-5: 排位将每个赛季重置一次
home.row7-6: 排位靠前的玩家将在每个赛季结束时获得专属饰品

powers.sorceryForDummies_Description: Has a chance to upgrade a random spell on your team every round (includes any unequipped spells). Cannot upgrade the same spell consecutive times. Chance scales with shop level.
powers.greevilsGreed_Description: Your gold never resets. For every 10 gold saved at the end of combat, you gain 1 additional gold.
powers.unstableConcoction_Description: Every round loss will gain a charge to this ability. Any win resets the charges to 0. If the charges reach 3, you will take 15% current HP in damage and the charges will reset to 0. Charges can not be less than 0.
powers.bloodrage_Description: Each ally hero death will enfrenzy selected unit with attack speed and lifesteal.
powers.sorceryVolumeThree_Description: Ultimates never enter your pool of spells. Shop scales differently than other Gods.
powers.bileExplosion_Description: Ally heroes will explode on death dealing damage in area. Damage dealt is a percentage of the damage taken that round. After exploding, a puddle of bile will remain on the ground that will cause enemies to take extra damage. Debuff is stackable.
powers.retaliate_Description: Selected hero will gain HP per round. They will also return a percent of damage dealt by physical attack. When a new hero is selected, the entire HP buff moves to them.
powers.shallowGrave_Description: Cast Shallow Grave on the first ally to fall within 20% HP threshold. Duration is based on shop level.
powers.cheatingDeath_Description: Your god will survive a death blow (goes down to 1 hp).
powers.sorceryVolumeTwo_Description: Heroes can use multiple ultimates, but shop upgrades are more expensive
powers.allIn_Description: Before your next fight, make a bet. If you win the next round, gain gold in the next shopping phase. If you lose, you get less gold for the following round. The amount of gold is a range of values based on a your shop level.
powers.wisdomOfTheElders_Description: Ability cooldowns now pause between rounds, but all abilities have cooldown reduction. Cooldown reduction scales with shop level.
powers.preyOnTheWeak_Description: Selected hero gains 9 attack speed for each ally summon. Summons gain half of this value. You will not lose attack speed if any summons die.
powers.hymnOfStCrella_Description: When selected hero dies, they will revive all dead allied heroes with reduced HP.
powers.stonehallPike_Description: Legion Commander God gains damage every round based on the total spell points your team has. Selected ally hero will gain this damage buff.
powers.feast_Description: Upon winning a round, Lifestealer heals himself (can overheal with no limit).
powers.multicast_Description: Selected unit has a chance to multicast a spell. The chance is tied to the amount of total spell points your team has.
powers.veiledPact_Description: Your units have a chance to deal a critical strike to enemies. They gain crit damage per number of units they travel. This buff lasts the entire round.
powers.beefyBoy_Description: Your God has more starting health.
powers.oathed_Description: Selected hero is silenced and has bonus damage. If selected unit is revived successfully, the damage buff is doubled.
powers.assault_Description: When an Oathed hero is killed, they will be revived after a delay with reduced HP as long as another ally hero is still alive. When revived, they will respawn in the back of the arena. Each revival will add an additional delay to the respawn time. Timer resets each round.
powers.darkMoonBlessing_Description: Ally heroes gain 0.04% spell amplification per 1 mana used. Buff resets every round.
powers.letsMakeADeal_Description: You can only upgrade your shop to level 3, but all spells cost 2 gold (and sell for 1). The amount of spells that appear in your shop is also reduced to 2/3/4.
powers.warmonger_Description: Sorla Khan deals more damage to other Gods for each surviving ally hero. For every damage she has dealt, her team gains a stacking attack damage buff.
powers.rearm_Description: Every round, re-rolls have reduced cost until you buy something or you re-roll a certain amount of times.
powers.fillBottle_Description: Selected unit will gain a random rune every round. Can gain multiple runes as the shop level increases.
powers.questionMark_Description: Both allies and enemies take magical damage per second.
powers.spellSteal_Description: Selected unit gains Spell Steal, which upgrades based on how many total spell points you have. Spell Steal does not count towards your four spell hero limit.
